<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.9.4">
<l>ciṅkama tāyavu ṇaṉtiṟa lākamuṉ kīṇṭukanta</l>
<l>paṅkaya māmalark kaṇpara ṉaiyempa rañcuṭarai</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷnaṉ māmukil cērtiru māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>naṅkaḷpi rāṉaiyiṉ ṟunaṇu kuṅkoleṉ naṉṉutalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will my [girl] with a fine forehead now be united with our lord</l>
<l>Who stands in Tirumāliruñcōlai with fine, dark clouds in the moonlight,</l>
<l>Our heavenly light, the supreme whose eyes are huge lotus blossoms,</l>
<l>Who as a lion was content, having once split the powerful chest of the demon?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
